title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: PA & Charch in studio! Golf.com's Josh Berhow breaks down The Open at Carnoustie. Pro Football HOF president/CEO Dave Baker talks about Randy Moss' induction, TO's decision to not attend and more. Tons of Vikings conversation throughout!
